title: The Rocky Horror Show LIVE Gala Performance 2015 720p.HDTV.x264-
description:
BBC America celebrates the 40th anniversary global tour of the original international hit, The Rocky Horror Show. A special midnight premiere of a brand new two-hour gala performance from the stage of London's Playhouse Theatre, starring original show creator, Richard O'Brien as 'The Narrator', and guest 'Narrators' Stephen Fry, Anthony Head, Adrian Edmondson, Emma Bunton and Mel Giedroyc.




Original Air Date: 17-Oct-2015
